  given invoke-read-graphвҶ’edges вүЎ [...]
  yield ready-cells-1[], blocked-cells-1[]

  вҲҙ config is frozen with topic вүЎ "the moon".
    poet: given configвҶ’topic вҖ” NOW BOUND (config frozen) вҶ’ READY
    scientist: given configвҶ’topic вҖ” NOW BOUND вҶ’ READY
    child: given configвҶ’topic вҖ” NOW BOUND вҶ’ READY
    combine: given poetвҶ’poem, scientistвҶ’fact, childвҶ’question вҖ” all still unbound вҶ’ BLOCKED

