-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= pick-cell-1
  given invoke-check-inputs-1вҶ’ready-cells-1 вүЎ [poet, scientist, child]
  yield В§target-1

  вҠў= В§target-1 вҶҗ poet

  yield В§target-1 вүЎ poet

вҠў evaluate-poet
  given pick-cell-1вҶ’В§target-1 вүЎ poet
  yield tentative-outputs-1[]

  вҲҙ Evaluate poet's вҲҙ body: "Write a haiku about В«configвҶ’topicВ»"
    with configвҶ’topic вүЎ "the moon".

-- LLM evaluation (poet is a soft cell):
-- Generating haiku about "the moon"...
-- Checking 5-7-5 syllable constraint...

  yield tentative-outputs-1 вүЎ [poem вүЎ "Silver crescent glows\nAbove the whispering pines\nNight breathes, soft and still"]

вҠў spawn-claims-1
  given evaluate-poetвҶ’tentative-outputs-1 вүЎ [poem вүЎ "Silver crescent glows\n..."]
  given pick-cell-1вҶ’В§target-1 вүЎ poet
  yield В§claim-cells-1[]

  вҲҙ poet has two oracles. Spawn two claim cells.

  yield В§claim-cells-1 вүЎ [
    В§claim-poet-1: { check: "poem is exactly 3 lines", type: structural },
    В§claim-poet-2: { check: "poem follows 5-7-5 syllable pattern", type: semantic }
  ]

вҠў check-claims-1
  given spawn-claims-1вҶ’В§claim-cells-1 вүЎ [В§claim-poet-1, В§claim-poet-2]
  yield all-pass-1, failed-oracles-1[]

  вҲҙ В§claim-poet-1: "Silver crescent glows\nAbove the whispering pines\nNight breathes, soft and still"
    Split on \n вҶ’ 3 lines вҶ’ вң“

    В§claim-poet-2: Syllable count:
      "Sil-ver cres-cent glows" вҶ’ 5 вң“
      "A-bove the whis-per-ing pines" вҶ’ 7 вң“
      "Night breathes, soft and still" вҶ’ 5 вң“

  yield all-pass-1 вүЎ true
  yield failed-oracles-1 вүЎ []

вҠў= decide-1
  given check-claims-1вҶ’all-pass-1 вүЎ true
  yield action-1

  вҠў= action-1 вҶҗ "freeze"

  yield action-1 вүЎ "freeze"

