--
-- вҠў config    вҶ’ topic вүЎ "the moon"                           [h1]
-- вҠў poet      вҶ’ poem вүЎ "Silver crescent glows\n..."          [h2]
-- вҠў scientist вҶ’ fact вүЎ "The Moon is drifting away..."         [h3]
-- вҠў child     вҶ’ question вүЎ "Why does the moon follow me..."  [h4]
-- вҠў= combine  вҶ’ document вүЎ "POEM:\n...\nFACT:\n...\n..."    [h5]
