-- Hash chain: h0 вҶ’ h1 вҶ’ h2 вҶ’ h3 вҶ’ h4 вҶ’ h5 (quiescent)
-- Each hi = content-address of the full document state after frame i.

-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- OBSERVATIONS
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ

вҠў= obs-metacircular
  yield observation

  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "cell-zero's eval-one loop executed p1-parallel-confluence in 5 eval-one steps (frames 4-6, 8-11), each cycling through cell-zero's phases: check-inputs вҶ’ pick-cell вҶ’ evaluate вҶ’ spawn-claims вҶ’ check-claims вҶ’ decide. The outer exerciser cells (frames 0-3) set up the evaluation context. This two-level structure demonstrates metacircular execution: a Cell program (cell-zero) evaluating another Cell program (p1-parallel-confluence), traced as a third Cell program (this exerciser)."

вҠў= obs-confluence
  yield observation

  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "After config froze, {poet, scientist, child} became simultaneously ready. Confluence (eval_diamond, proven in Lean) guarantees any permutation produces the same combineвҶ’document. We traced poetвҶ’scientistвҶ’child, but all 6 orderings converge to identical h5. This is the parallel execution guarantee: cell-zero could spawn 3 parallel evaluations and the result would be the same."

вҠў= obs-fusion
  yield observation

  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "cell-zero's evaluate phase correctly dispatched based on cell type. config: pass-through (given вүЎ values become yield вүЎ values). poet, scientist, child: soft cells вҖ” вҲҙ bodies interpreted by LLM substrate. combine: hard cell вҖ” вҠў= body computed deterministically. This is the fusion property: Cell requires both classical and semantic substrates working together."

вҠў= obs-oracle-claim-protocol
  yield observation

  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "10 oracle checks across 5 eval-one steps. Each step spawned claim cells (cell-zero.spawn-claims) that checked tentative outputs before freezing. Oracle types exercised: semantic (noun phrase, factual accuracy, simple vocabulary), structural (line count, question mark, contains-all). The claim cell protocol means oracles are just more cells in the graph вҖ” no special machinery."

вҠў= obs-state-is-document
  yield observation

  вҠў= observation вҶҗ "The target program's state at each step IS the document with more yield вүЎ bindings filled in. h0: no bindings. h5: all bindings. Each eval-one step changes exactly one yield line вҖ” this is the document-is-state property. Content addressing makes each state a unique hash. The trace is a hash chain: h0вҶ’h1вҶ’h2вҶ’h3вҶ’h4вҶ’h5."
